{
 "name": "RPlog_SW1_Log_2000-01-11",
 "title": "An Offer in the OREO Boardroom",
 "summary": "In the OREO board meeting room high above Corellia's capital, the ambitious magnate John Donivan summons Bazil McKenzie, a former independent pilot recently transferred from Star Ops into the New Republic Diplomatic Corps. Over glasses of cognac, Donivan probes the disillusioned pilot about his career, his dissatisfaction, and his desires, drawing out Bazil's admission that he chases wealth and freedom rather than medals. Satisfied that he has read his man, Donivan proposes a discreet arrangement: in exchange for generous compensation, Bazil would feed him restricted information gathered through his diplomatic posting. Bazil, masking his interest behind diplomatic poise, agrees to keep the conversation secret and signals his willingness to deal, though he notes his low rank has so far yielded little of value.",
